def is_in_dining_room(item: item):
    # Function to check if an item is in the dining room
    symbol in_dining_room = exists room: item : is_dining_room(room) and inside(item, room)
    return in_dining_room

def is_knive_near_cutting_board(knife:item):
    # Function to verify if a knife is close to a cutting board
    symbol knife_near_cutting_board = exists board: item : is_cutting_board(board) and close(knife, 
board)
    return knife_near_cutting_board

behavior cut_kiwi_and_add_to_cup(kiwi:item, knife:item, cup:item):
    body:
        if is_knive_near_cutting_board(knife):
            achieve cut(kiwi)
            # Cut the kiwi if the knife is near the cutting board
        achieve inside(kiwi, cup)
        # Add the sliced kiwi to the cup

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        assert exists cup: item : is_cup(cup) and has_water(cup)
        # The cup must already have water as per the completed subtask
        
        bind kiwi: item where:
            is_food_kiwi(kiwi) and is_in_dining_room(kiwi)
        # Select a kiwi that is in the dining room

        bind knife: item where:
            is_knife(knife) and is_knive_near_cutting_board(knife)
        # Select a knife that is near a cutting board in the dining room
        
        bind cup: item where:
            is_cup(cup) and has_water(cup)
        # Select a cup that already has water

        cut_kiwi_and_add_to_cup(kiwi, knife, cup)
        # Execute the behavior to slice the kiwi and add it to the cup with water

behavior clean_food(food:item, sink:item):
    body:
        achieve_once inside(food, sink)
        # Ensure the food is placed inside the sink

        if is_faucet(sink):
            bind faucet: item where:
                is_faucet(faucet) and close(faucet,sink)
            achieve_once is_on(faucet)
            # If the sink has a faucet, turn it on to clean

        wash(food) # This is the key step of the behavior, used for cleaning food
        
        if is_faucet(sink):
            bind faucet: item where:
                is_faucet(faucet) and close(faucet,sink)
            achieve_once is_off(faucet)
            # If the sink has a faucet, turn it off after cleaning

behavior cut_food(kiwi:item, knife:item, cutting_board:item):
    body:
        achieve on(kiwi, cutting_board) # Place the kiwi on the cutting board
        achieve cut(kiwi) # Slice the kiwi with the knife

behavior put_in_cup(kiwi:item, cup:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(kiwi, cup) # Add the kiwi to the cup

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind kiwi: item where:
            is_food_kiwi(kiwi)
        bind sink: item where:
            is_sink(sink)
        bind knife: item where:
            is_knife(knife)
        bind cutting_board: item where:
            is_cutting_board(cutting_board)
        bind cup: item where:
            is_cup(cup) and has_water(cup) # Ensure the cup has water

        clean_food(kiwi, sink) # Clean the kiwi in the sink
        cut_food(kiwi, knife, cutting_board) # Slice the kiwi
        put_in_cup(kiwi, cup) # Add the sliced kiwi to the cup with water
